intent 传递的是数据
example:
send data:
	Intent kip_to = new Intent(getActivity(), Activity.class);
	Bundle bundle = new Bundle();
	bundle.putInt("freeze", freeze);
	bundle.putString("countryNum", countryNum);
	bundle.putString("phoneNum", phoneNum);
	kip_to.putExtras(bundle);

get data:
	Intent intent = getActivity().getIntent();
	mFreeze = intent.getIntExtra("freeze", 0);
	mPhone = intent.getStringExtra("phoneNum");
	mCountry = intent.getStringExtra("countryNum");
	
bundle 传递的是对象
example:
send data:
	A a = new A();
	Bundle bundle = new Bundle();
	bundle.putSerializable(ITEM, item);
	a.setArguments(bundle);
	// 这里的a可以展示成dialog,也可以跳转
	// BUYSERVICEITEM传递的标识
	
get data:
	Bundle bundle = this.getArguments();
	if (bundle != null) {
		Item item = (Item) bundle.getSerializable(
				ITEM);// 注意 ITEM 需一致
	}
